# Project Plan File Convention

When creating or updating implementation plans for this codebase:

- Do not store project plans only in Cursor's default user-level plan storage.
- Save all project-level plan manuscripts under:

  `docs/plans/manuscripts/`

- Use Markdown files.
- File naming convention:

  `YYYYMMDD-<short-topic>.md`

- Before implementation, create or update the relevant plan file first.
- If a plan already exists for the same topic, update the existing file instead of creating a duplicate.